        // About Section
        section#about.page-section.bg-primary.text-white.mb-0
            .container
                // About Section Heading
                h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-white About
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider-light
                    .divider-custom-line
                    .divider-custom-icon
                        i.fas.fa-moon
                    .divider-custom-line
                // About Section Content
                p.mb-2
                    | Hi there, I work as a detail-oriented mechanical engineer. Originally from Christchurch NZ, I have an eye for the true nature of a situation, the ability to define and choose the simplest practical solution. I take on responsibility early and work hard to deliver results. I have 3.5 years' work experience in a mix of automation engineering, project management and mechanical design. With my range of experience, I have proven my ability to adapt to different industries. I have consistently learnt new skills, quickly reaching the level where I can work self-sufficiently.
                p.mb-2
                    | I do enjoy working in a collaborative team environment. Co-workers have found me to be an enthusiastic, fun and thoughtful person to work with. I have done a range of team-oriented tasks such as designing interviews and interviewing candidates, mentoring new employees and project managing workload for a small team of engineers.
