                    | Outside of work I am an avid sportsman. I have a background in High performance sport. I Rowed for NZ competing all over the world then finished undergrad and postgrad on scholarship in the states. Half of my final crew went on to the Tokyo Olympics. Now I dive, ski bike and do most of the good kiwi outdoor sports. Considering getting into pack rafting. I enjoy modifying and making my own equipment for these sports, currently working on my own electric dive float to follow me around while diving. Thatâ€™s where you will find me on the weekend, getting after it in the wilderness or working on my own projects at home.
